entries.femaleVariant: What's it like to be a cop in Night City?
Well, what's it like bein' a criminal?
Excuse me? Was that an accusation?
Any honest cops out there?
You're asking me?
No clue.
Right... Forget it.
What, don't consider yourself one?
I, good sir, adhere to a code. It's not my fault it isn't always legal.
I wouldn't know. I'm no criminal.
Breaking the law is the literal definition of crime, V.
It's not my fault the law can't keep pace with reality.
You pluck one lowlife off the street two more sprout up in his place.
Plus, unless you're the rare idealist, you take bribes when you can get 'em.
And book-cooking? Amount of booze needed to drown your doubts gets pricey but, well... that's what the bribes're for.
Wow... exciting.
Pretty bleak.
Sounds... exhilarating.
So... a bleach caricature of life?
Twenty thousand killed or gone missing every year. Not exactly boring.
What it like, bein' a cop in Night City?
Which gang's the worst?
There even a single clean badge in this city?
Besides me?
An honest cop in Night City's like a unicorn.
That what you see when you look in the mirror?
But okay, I'd bet there's one or two more. Take Anna Hamill for example.
Wonder how she is now... It's been ages.
She won't take bribes?
What makes her different?
How, she won't pocket bribes?
How's she stand out?
She hounds down criminals on her own terms. Bit of a superhero complex.
She always places justice higher than the letter of the law. And won't follow her superiors blind.
Know someone just like that...
Which gang's the city's biggest and baddest according to the NCPD?
Scavs hold the body count title. Well, or Maelstrom – depending on the season.
How you getting along with Han?
Let's talk about something else.
Let's change the subject.
How're things with you and Han workin' out?
Didn't have any blowback? I mean for steppin' into the Peter Pan case.
How's the career switch? When's our new private detective startin' up?
Any trouble after the Peter Pan case?
How's the private detective career?
Not angry I haven't had any time for you?
Not too pissed I haven't had the time for you?
entries.maleVariant: Ya not too pissed I haven't had the time for ya?

entries.femaleVariant: No, it's only 'cause of us Gonaghal closed the investigation.
They padded their stat books, we're in the clear.
And? How do you feel 'bout all this?
I'll let you know once I know. For now I'm just helpin' out Joss, enjoyin' some time off...
Life should be back on track before long.
Still findin' the means. Hasn't been easy, but the biggest hurdles are behind me.
License, equipment, software – it's all in order. Just haven't figured out how to market myself...
Aimin' to specialize in anything?
Kidnapping. Randy's ordeal put a lot in perspective.
Well... Guess that makes sense.
They're not.
He acts like nothing happened, like he didn't cover up the mayor's death.
Must be tough...
I considered him a close partner. Maybe even a friend.
So yeah, you could say that.
I understand, let's change the subject.
You got your own stuff goin' on, I get that. We'll make up for it.
Yeah, promise. Soon as I cut some dead weight.
entries.maleVariant: As soon as I can cut some dead weight.

entries.femaleVariant: I'll hold you to it.
I don't feel things are right with us.
Been havin' this thought lately...
About what?
Us. Can't get it outta my head...
entries.maleVariant: Us. I can't get outta my head...

entries.femaleVariant: That you don't see a happy ending?
H-how'd you know?
I didn't. Maybe I'm just startin' to get to know you better.
Anyway, I... It's stupid. Rambling. Just forget I said anything.
entries.maleVariant: Anyway, I... It's stupid. I'm ramblin'. Just forget I said anything.

entries.femaleVariant: Already forgotten.
But I gotta give style points to the Valentinos. They have a punishment for every occasion.
Example – they sit you in front of a mirror with a shaving razor and tell you to keep goin' until red and pink turns to white.
Looking for a girl.
Lookin' for someone. Woman, twenty something. Doll, disappeared from Clouds.
Could scan the system, but... You even know how many girls disappear in this city every day?
'Specially the ones working in the sex biz. Don't get your hopes up.
What's on your mind, V?
All right, take care now.
